{"tid":781483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報社評：港獨提上國際層面 推香港進入死胡同","createTime":"2018-08-16T02:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T14:48:56.000Z","uid":92301,"like":3,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"23c6405e30c88e557b7f30015c7297a2de1e6986","tid":781483,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨召集人陳浩天應邀在外國記者會（下稱FCC）演講，高談港獨主張，特區政府和外交部駐港特派員公署分別發表聲明譴責。港獨否定一國兩制，破壞中央與香港關係，只會令香港陷入死胡同。FCC強調「支持香港及世界各地言論自由」、無意為港獨張目，惟觀乎整場演講，實際效果確是為宣揚港獨提供了平台，讓港獨有機會上升至國際層面，把香港緩緩推向大國外交角力漩渦之中，從政治現實主義角度而論，對香港有害無益。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>FCC演講變宣傳平台 陳浩天主張令人側目</strong><br />\n<br />\nFCC邀請陳浩天演講談「獨」激起政治波瀾，事件需要從政治理念和現實效果兩個角度考慮。連日來不少討論都將焦點放在言論自由等意識形態層面，有人認為中央和特區政府擺出強硬態度，會製造寒蟬效應、遏制言論自由，云云；有人則認為，即使在西方社會，言論自由一樣有界線，宣揚港獨顛覆憲制基礎，已超出言論自由界線。港獨倘若涉及具體違法行為，當然可以用法律處理，惟今次事件重點明顯在於政治層面。港人珍惜言論自由，對中央和特區政府一言一行特別敏感，絕對可以理解，惟「寒蟬效應」之說，有時也未免太過籠統空泛，反而妨礙深入討論。<br />\n<br />\n香港是開放社會，言論自由必須守護，惟放眼西方國家現實操作，言論自由確有界線。以英國為例，當局近年就以「遏抑極端主義」之名，採取不少措施，遏制激進伊斯蘭教士及新納粹分子。數年前英國一群跨黨派議員指稱，極端主義在英國大學校園蔓延，成為「嚴重問題」，部分大學「未能恰當平衡學術自由和國家安全」、拒絕跟情報機關合作。前首相卡梅倫甚至點名多間著名大學，批評校方容讓激進伊斯蘭教士宣揚仇恨「損害英國價值」，強調大學不應為這些人提供演講平台，必須「切斷他們茁莊發展所需的氧氣」。<br />\n<br />\n這些激進分子大多沒有拿起真刀真槍，惟經常發表煽動仇恨暴力的言論。前年英國政府查禁一個名為National Action的新納粹組織，原因並非它密謀武裝起義，而是該組織在社交媒體和大學校園宣揚仇恨暴力，鼓吹反猶和種族主義，揚言要全部驅逐少數族裔新移民，又「頌讚」殺害女議員考克斯的兇手。當然，人們永遠可以爭辯，甲地的做法，是否可以與乙地情况相提並論，由於英國是民主國家，香港沒有全面民主，所以「永不存在可比性」，然而現在問題正正是，言論自由確有界線，可是香港應該怎麼劃卻是言人人殊，很多人都是立場決定腦袋，一味形而上哲學爭辯，不考慮政治現實情况，當然是沒完沒了。<br />\n<br />\n回歸以來FCC與特區政府一直相安無事，外界未有任何確鑿證據，不應動輒訴諸陰謀論，隨便斷言FCC「別有用心」，然而不管用意動機，從現實政治角度考慮，FCC邀請陳浩天演講，的確是為港獨提供了一次面向國際的宣傳平台，肯定引來政治風波，甚至害了香港。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港言論自由需守護 捲入中美鬥爭要提防</strong><br />\n<br />\n目前中美貿易戰角力激烈，際此敏感時刻將港獨提上國際層次，後果可大可小。陳浩天演講揚言，「香港已失去獨特地位」，要求華府取消《香港關係法》，不再就經貿關稅事宜將內地和香港區分處理。陳浩天的倡議，簡言之就是呼籲美國拿香港作為棋子，為求打擊內地，不惜犧牲香港利益，最令人憂慮是如果華府政客真的認為有機可乘，順水推舟，香港有可能深陷中美鬥爭漩渦。中央為阻外國加強介入香港事務暗助港獨，有可能進一步大幅收緊對港政策，到時香港不僅經濟受累，連政治空間也可能受擠壓。這對香港肯定是禍不是福。<br />\n<br />\n誠然，香港民族黨面臨查禁，陳浩天成為新聞人物，有採訪價值，然而傳媒角色從來不是做傳聲筒。傳媒專業對於一個爭議題目，不會只讓事件一方發聲，還會力求平衡，公平處理另一邊聲音，有時是一則報道內兼陳正反觀點，有時是透過多則報道尋求綜合平衡。可是FCC整場演講，大體就是讓陳浩天高談港獨理念，問答環節主要也是讓他闡述看法，多於觀點交鋒。10多條提問，只有一條問他「可以怎樣實踐其政治主張」較為尖銳。設若本港也有智庫團體，邀請英國政界口中的極端主義者來港演講，講解為何要向西方報復，又或為納粹德國屠殺猶太人塗脂抹粉，恐怕事件很快便會變成外交風波。<br />\n<br />\n部分港獨分子喜歡堆砌一些學術概念，諸如「公民民族主義」等，作為港獨理據，陳浩天演講大抵也是循此思路，一邊以追求民主包裝港獨，更說「反對暴力」。這些說辭也許可以討好一些外國聽眾，不過香港民族黨過去鼓吹武力鬥爭、散播仇恨和歧視內地人言論，諸如「中國人乃香港社會問題的根源，只有中國人在港絕迹，香港人才能安居樂業」等民粹論述，口脗倒跟當年魏瑪德國極右分子揚言「清除猶太人」如出一轍，單是這一點，香港社會便應該保持高度警惕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180815/s00003/1534270719304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180815%2Fs00003%2F1534270719304&d=0MmRsDG7u40qM6sWtv%2BP654f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5d5fdf83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180815%2Fs00003%2F1534270719304&h=090ea838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180815/s00003/1534270719304</a>"},{"pid":"43bf6af998741d4301d71cc2324c57e576019f5a","tid":781483,"uid":26506,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"關鍵時刻明報又明目張膽露底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b62e55bb01b19d6b74483a8b663a575e15f320d","tid":781483,"uid":58552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"要麼獨立<br />\n要麼一國一制"},{"pid":"762f53f80c5c0b83efa4739b1febd36975e4e44e","tid":781483,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"唔巧激嬲中共牙～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc59442c1ccecfa468038f17bc093ed2abb2b3c","tid":781483,"uid":156652,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"你講撚左中共又係西,,,唔講又係西,,,老西都講"},{"pid":"c47053770187c6cec7342bb7339ca98f261dfba6","tid":781483,"uid":41116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"又攞d 民主公開透明嘅國家同自己個極權黑箱作業垃圾國比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84442651e9f9cad3cfb34475b84ef91189547555","tid":781483,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"就係燒埋落班港豬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf916c29d5c834285f9c91f7f8c35ed94a144988","tid":781483,"uid":87600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"唔提咪又係死<br />\n最好就攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e3e4118c52f632bba7640440d55487432c74cd","tid":781483,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"都唔好講政治空間收窄係未有港獨已經開始<br />\nd 評論都話香港經濟佔比已經少左好多，無必要再比太多空間香港<br />\n你走去賴港獨會搞到收窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b96017a6dcfe96de04054d61eac100300c08c1","tid":781483,"uid":60366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:08:12.000Z","msg":"又係依啲陰啲陰啲將港獨同Nazi比較嘅偷換概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗱，港獨依個政治概念本身係中性，<br />\n成個理念個根源就係 &quot;將香港成為一個獨立於其他政體嘅主權國家&quot;, 就係咁簡單<br />\n如果只係因為港獨派入面有部份on9仔話要趕哂啲中國人走，所以就要警剔港獨/ 唔比討論/唔理三七廿一ban柒哂拉柒哂班人，<br />\n依樣係件好撚on9同無理嘅事<br />\n<br />\n而Nazism 根本係性質上就係另外一樣野黎<br />\n佢個概念源頭由第一日開始就係種族優越論同種族隔離主義"},{"pid":"ab19dcb5ba85d19aa085aed47ea5fdfd59549138","tid":781483,"uid":40216,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"共產黨話你係法西斯就代表你做得非常正確"},{"pid":"6d2908a3ea7ef71c2c526c5a9a1201a16a0b8f29","tid":781483,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗講咁多<br />\n中共快做回自己，派人來香港暗殺陳浩天啦"},{"pid":"8193db5dfa51812a63dad3a4ea7f7ac6216d1f4d","tid":781483,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"屌 陳浩天呢d 撚樣咪又係呃飯食"},{"pid":"670b0cf3895a33732a16238c65b1561a1fda0cd9","tid":781483,"uid":17103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.thinkingtaiwan.com/sites/default/files/images/insert/policy/5cb03927986c62210733ba8728eee173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkingtaiwan.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Finsert%2Fpolicy%2F5cb03927986c62210733ba8728eee173.jpg&h=8e2661ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e4dc0e673899d39c6feb3ae76f8427ba5f1caa2","tid":781483,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"你睇lee兩日班五毛幾撚勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42aa322312b8ef87ff54a77b4a4c4d0a1d89238","tid":781483,"uid":185085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"670b0cf3895a33732a16238c65b1561a1fda0cd9","tid":781483,"uid":17103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.thinkingtaiwan.com/sites/default/files/images/insert/policy/5cb03927986c62210733ba8728eee173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkingtaiwan.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Finsert%2Fpolicy%2F5cb03927986c62210733ba8728eee173.jpg&h=8e2661ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"中共反對的 就證明我地做啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dedb73a8e38a530200799ff61a84f8eb1f1084","tid":781483,"uid":11895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"又講到唔反抗支共就唔會搞尻你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454eeac1ebde861889de77ca4c1526768dc19d39","tid":781483,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"老共好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133cac12dd1271b918f35ca0beafdd3d7f465497","tid":781483,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1e12473ac264d79237f3eb43cd9ad0e230e3652","tid":781483,"uid":35021,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"133cac12dd1271b918f35ca0beafdd3d7f465497","tid":781483,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0Iyau7QcKtKUYIda/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0Iyau7QcKtKUYIda%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e4943d2f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}